    <div class="container">  
      <h3>Conclusion</h3>
      <p>That's all you need to do to include more mazes.  The mazes will just loop in a cyclic fashion as the levels increase.  Well, that was an easy section.  It's nice to end a phase on an easy section I think.  Now we can officially move on to phase 2.  So in the next section we'll discuss how to add graphics.  We'll start with the basics first by adding the graphics that will display an image of the Pacman character in place of the yellow circles indicating the number of lives left.</p>

